  ### Who can get legal aid?

  * your income (or combined income if you have a partner) should not
    be more than £2,657 a month before tax
  * your savings (or combined savings if you have a partner) should not
    be more than £8,000
  * your income (or combined income if you have a partner) after certain
    outgoings have been deducted must not be more than £733 a month -
    this service will ask you more about these outgoings
